{"tid":1570806,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"1645 警方將於中環及金鐘展開驅散行動","createTime":"2019-09-15T08:51:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-15T08:53:27.000Z","uid":41404,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"55d4266c6a1f75406100b2a1be2817482f0d45d3","tid":1570806,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T08:51:22.000Z","msg":"電台及電視台當值宣布員注意：<br />\n <br />\n請盡快播出下列消息，並在適當時間重播：<br />\n <br />\n     今日（九月十五日）下午四時半開始，激進示威者於中環及金鐘多處縱火，亦有激進示威者破壞並堵塞金鐘站的出入口。夏慤道近政府總部的來回行車線亦被堵塞。<br />\n <br />\n     警方將會在短時間內驅散示威者。警方警告示威者立刻停止所有違法行為，並離開現場。市民應避免前往金鐘、中環一帶。<br />\n <br />\n完<br />\n2019年9月15日（星期日）<br />\n香港時間16時45分"},{"pid":"346c013e2905d11ddc26a7976b0df9b43d6ed126","tid":1570806,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T08:51:41.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/201909/15/P2019091500538.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.info.gov.hk%2Fgia%2Fgeneral%2F201909%2F15%2FP2019091500538.htm&d=xWOcOck8MQRdM6xM79L4mFyVYJ%2BaYT2AGLfERhQaW2c%3D&h=374b7107\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/201909/15/P2019091500538.htm</a>"},{"pid":"cd6cd48cd38b28aa5eccbc32de9247163a576671","tid":1570806,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T08:51:56.000Z","msg":"港鐵金鐘站暫時關閉 列車不停金鐘站<br />\n2019-09-15 HKT 16:49<br />\n港鐵表示，因應金鐘站外的突發情況，經風險評估，為確保乘客、員工及鐵路設施安全，港島綫、荃灣綫、南港島綫現時不停金鐘站，車站暫時關閉。"},{"pid":"18396aa2df8fb2bae65f029ec86cdcacd6096cea","tid":1570806,"uid":53062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T08:53:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}